data.description: Welcome to your ideal 3-bed, 2-bath home in Byron, GA! This 1721 sq ft gem features a freshly painted interior, a spacious living area, and a modern kitchen with ample counter space. The bedrooms offer comfort and privacy, with the master boasting an ensuite bathroom.  Step outside to the covered back porch, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the outdoors. The property also includes a garage for secure parking and extra storage.  Conveniently located in a peaceful neighborhood, this home is close to amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss the chance to make 123 Alexis Way your own-schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and style this home has to offer!
